; Coverage test for account.cc get_cost throwing an error (L282-285).
; In account context, 'cost' is not a valid field and throws an error.
; Also exercises the 'c' case in account_t::lookup (L419-424).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --format "%(cost)\n" -> 1
__ERROR__
While calculating format expression:
  cost
While evaluating value expression:
  cost
Error: An account does not have a 'cost' value
end test
